{"id":604397,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/【立此存照】人民日报呼吁转发钓鱼岛微博-评/","date":"2019-01-22T11:23:58Z","modified":"2019-01-22T11:23:58Z","title":"【立此存照】人民日报呼吁转发“钓鱼岛”微博 评论翻车","content":"<p>1月21日，人民日报新浪微博发布“钓鱼岛，中国的！”相关微博，进行“微博抗日”，并希望网友转发“传递真相”，然而该微博未及时限制网友评论，导致评论区“翻车”。目前，人民日报已关闭<a href=\"https://weibo.com/2803301701/HcVhSbPCp\">该微博</a>下的网友最新评论显示。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/0075aK2Pgy1fzfkdv93mdj30k05777wh.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-604398\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/0075aK2Pgy1fzfkdv93mdj30k05777wh.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"5148\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/0075aK2Pgy1fzfkdv93mdj30k05777wh.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/0075aK2Pgy1fzfkdv93mdj30k05777wh-32x300.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9807,9249,8620,37708,20434,37709,14208]}